<h2 id="can-i-logout">Can I Logout? <a class="headerlink" href="logout-and-last-username#can-i-logout" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Next challenge! Can we logout? Um... right now? Nope! But that seems important! So,
let's do it.</p>
<p>Start like normal: In <code>SecurityController</code>, create a <code>logoutAction</code>, set its route
to <code>/logout</code> and call the route <code>security_logout</code>:</p>
