<p>Perfect!</p>
<p>Try the <em>whole</em> thing out: head to the homepage. We're anonymous right now.. so let's
login! Cool! And there's the logout link. Click it! Ok, back to anonymous. If you
need to control what happens after logging out, check the official docs on the logout
stuff.</p>
<p>Alright. Now, as much as I like turtles, we should <em>probably</em> give our users a real
password.</p>

    
