	                                <p>Hey Yang,</p><p>Use global `app` variable to access user object, i.e. {{ app.user.username }}. But ensure your user is authenticated, otherwise you'll get an error:<br></p><pre>{% if is_granted('IS_AUTHENTICATED_ANONYMOUSLY') %}<br>     &lt;li&gt;Login...&lt;/li&gt;<br>{% else %}<br>    &lt;li&gt;&lt; a href="{{ path('security_logout') }}"&gt;Logout&lt;/li&gt;<br>{% endif %}<br></pre><p></p><p>Cheers!</p>
